 MuCh/RICH section of the beam pipe with conical shape have 
 half opening angle 2.5deg. TRD-ToF section is composed of cylinder 
 with R161.1mm, PSD section with R95mm 
 and with 5 cm shift in XZ plane relative to the beam direction

 Detailed information find at https://cbm-wiki.gsi.de/foswiki/pub/PWG/C2F/BeamPipe/20180530_Internal_Note_beam_pipe-AS.pdf

